result.name: Yuen Kee Dessert

reviews.text:
What can I say about this old style Chinese dessert place?  Yum.  Their famous dessert is 桑寄生蓮子茶 (sang parasitic lotus seed tea) $35.  They've been around for over 100 years.
So now in 2019 it's up to $37.... Still good

If you are looking for authentic local dessert, this IS the right place. All time favourites include "Dark Tea Egg with Lotus Seeds", "Green beans soup", "Seaseme thick soup". If you know what I'm talking about, you know where to go.

Serving traditional chinese desserts, mainly sweet soup prepared in traditional way. Something traditional is still the best approach. Service up to 11.00 pm and there is always a line waiting as there is only 20+ seats after 9.00. Their only non soup dessert is a Chinese steam cake with egg which is surprisingly good and worth trying.

Traditional chinese dessert soup house with a history of over 100 years.  It's famous mulberry mistletoe soup with lotus seeds is just too great! I used to come here with my family when I am still a child. Lots of memories there.

Good Song Kee Sang dessert soup, almond milk soup, walnut milk soup for dessert. The shop has over 100 years of history. Song Kee Sang has Chinese medicinal properties (good for back pains, digestion).  Almond milk and walnut milk dessert soup are good for skin.

reviews.text: 雞蛋茶👍
很久沒有吃到沒有加杏仁精的杏仁露，有點感動。芝麻糊和核桃露真的都很棒，雞蛋糕就稍嫌乾，不是我的喜歡。
名過於實,性價比低,水準非常ㄧ般,排隊衹為名氣。
蓮子杏仁茶好味，蓮子鷄蛋合桃露好味，桑寄生蛋茶仲好味，尤其係用桑寄生煙燻嘅蛋好味到食咗兩隻啊！
幾十年的老店，出品可以保持質素，非常難得！我也光顧了30多年，別有一番風味，店員都全換過了，服務質素比以前好，5星！！
